; Regression test for issue #577: Error in automated virtual postings with multiple commodities (BZ#577)
; https://github.com/ledger/ledger/issues/577
;
; Ledger previously threw an error when automated transactions generated virtual
; postings for transactions involving multiple commodities. Both per-transaction
; and across separate transactions with different commodities should work.

